    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271433>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Tripylella mexicana sp. n. Female (A. D). A: Cephalic region, dorsal view; B: Annuli with anastomoses, somatic setae and body pores; C: Vulva, latero-ventral view; D: Tail, lateral view." ;
